high_descs: Walk forward then turn to the left. Then go forward to the counter and turn right to face it.
Pick up the butter knife off of the counter.
Turn to the left then right then left again to the brown shelf.
Place the knife inside of the green cup on the shelf.
Pick up the green cup with the knife inside.
Turn to the right and go forward. Turn right again and go to the counter top. Turn left to face the counter top.
Place the green cup and knife on to the counter.
anns.task_desc: Move a knife and a green cup to the counter.

high_descs: Go toward the wall, then turn left and go in between the chairs, then turn left to face the kitchen island.
Pick up the rightmost butter knife on the kitchen island.
Turn around and move forward, then go to the shelves to your right.
Put the butter knife in the green cup on the top shelf.
Pick up the green cup from the top shelf.
Turn right and go towards the wall, then turn right at the refrigerator and go forward, then turn left to face the dishwasher.
Put the green cup on the counter above the dishwasher.
anns.task_desc: Put a green cup with a butter knife in it on the counter.

high_descs: Walk towards the wall, then hang a left and walk towards the window, turn left and walk up to the kitchen island.
Pick up the rightmost butter knife off of the kitchen island in front of you.
Turn around and walk forward, then hang a right and walk over to the wooden shelving unit against the wall.
Put the butter knife in the green cup on the top shelf of the wooden shelving unit.
Pick up the green cup with the butter knife in it.
Turn right and walk forward, then hang a right and walk over to the counter where the toaster is.
Put the green cup with the butter knife in it on the counter in front of the golden statue.
anns.task_desc: Put a green cup with a butter knife in it on the counter.
